  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6827.75 trading below the GEX flip at 6834, dealers are positioned to buy any further dips as they're long gamma in this PIN regime. The massive positive gamma wall at 6850 (+6.6B) creates strong resistance where dealers will aggressively sell rallies, while the negative gamma pocket at 6820 (-2.5B) provides support through dealer buying. The recent GEX surge combined with the current setup suggests dealers will actively dampen volatility and defend the 6820-6850 range.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect price to get pinned between 6820-6850 with limited breakout potential.",
